Class UserAwayMessageEvent

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClientLinked, ActorEvent<User>, ClientEvent, ServerMessageEvent

    public class UserAwayMessageEvent
extends ActorEventBase<User>
    A User has changed away status, informed via AWAY message. Note that two events may fire in a row while the user remains away, just with a changed message.
